Prerequisites for building from sources:
        mupdf         [http://mupdf.com/]
        ocaml (4.06+) [http://ocaml.org/]
        opengl        [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenGL]
        git           [https://git-scm.com/]

  llpp% git clone git://git.ghostscript.com/mupdf.git --recursive
  llpp% cd mupdf
  mupdf% git checkout e7cc5e1de83302579bc6aabcf132a9d269f7e5f8
  mupdf% git submodule update --recursive
  mupdf% make build=native libs
  mupdf% cd ..
  llpp% sh build.sh build

Standalone binary should now be in build/llpp

Native macOS Installation Instructions
--------------------------------------

  If `sh build.sh build' succeeds, standalone macOS app should be in
  build/llpp.app.
